title: Mets 2B Murphy homers in 5th straight postseason game (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,415 Mets 2B Murphy homers in 5th straight postseason game (Yahoo Sports) CHICAGO (AP) -- Mets second baseman Daniel Murphy has homered for the fifth consecutive postseason game, matching the major league record.
